snippet.title: Chef's Luv Shack [PS1] 1/3
snippet.description: I had all 3 South Park games on the PS1 and I'll have to admit this one I still kinda like.  On your own it's boring and short even on hot and heavy but at least it doesn't have the sound of puking dolls and gobbling turkeys.
